  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is performed to investigate the long-term safety, in particular the diabetogenic
      potential and immunogenicity of rhGH therapy in short children born small for gestational age
      (SGA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
